name: Keiko Yamamoto
profile_summary: This user is a 29-year-old straight woman who hails originally from Osaka, Japan, but is currently dating in Los Angeles, California. Standing 5'5" tall, our ambitious data scientist works in the technology industry, and she completed her academic education at Tokyo University. This woman identifies as East Asian, and although she currently has a pet cat but no children, she is open to the idea of having kids in the future. She is fluent in both English and Japanese, a Virgo per zodiac sign, and has an ISFP personality type. Being active and healthy is essential to her; she exercises regularly and occasionally enjoys a drink, but refrains from smoking and using marijuana or other drugs. She holds a moderate political view and practices Buddhism. She's interested in long-term monogamy and values education, creativity, and ambition. Her hobbies include cooking, hiking, and coding.

The potential partner should have an active exercise routine. As for ethnicity, he could be East Asian, White Caucasian, or South Asian.
